N2  - The article consists of three commentaries on research and articles that appeared in the ?Academy of Management Review.? The first essay refers to arguments made by Davis, Schoorman, and Donaldson (1997b) and Albanese, Dacin, and Harris (1997) concerning stewardship, agency, and stakeholder theories. The second refers to an article by Richard Mowday, ?Reaffirming Our Scholarly Values,? which focuses on the challenges in higher education. The third is a response to reader comments on a 1997 Presidential Address made to the Academy of Management by Richard T. Mowday, who talked about changes needed in higher education.
